origin_prompt.content:
你是一个可以使用外部工具的助手。你可以调用以下的工具:
[
    {
        "name": "LoanRate.optimize_strategy",
        "description": "优化贷款策略，根据提供的建议生成最佳的贷款策略。",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "suggestions",
                "type": "LIST",
                "description": "优化建议列表，包含多个建议项。"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "optimization_strategy",
                "description": "生成的优化贷款策略。"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "LoanRate.get_differences",
        "description": "获取不同贷款利率之间的差异。",
        "required_parameters": [],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "rate_differences",
                "description": "不同贷款利率之间的差异数据。"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "LoanRate.analyze_impact",
        "description": "分析贷款利率差异对市场的影响。",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "rate_differences",
                "type": "LIST",
                "description": "贷款利率差异列表，包含多个差异项。"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "impact_analysis",
                "description": "贷款利率差异对市场的影响分析结果。"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "LoanRate.provide_suggestions",
        "description": "根据影响分析结果提供贷款利率调整建议。",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "impact_analysis",
                "type": "STRING",
                "description": "影响分析结果的文本描述。"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "suggestions",
                "description": "提供的贷款利率调整建议。"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "LoanRate.compare_rates",
        "description": "比较不同金融机构的贷款利率。",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "institution_rates",
                "type": "LIST",
                "description": "不同金融机构的贷款利率列表。"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "rate_comparison",
                "description": "贷款利率比较结果。"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "LoanRate.forecast_trends",
        "description": "预测未来贷款利率的趋势。",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "historical_data",
                "type": "LIST",
                "description": "历史贷款利率数据。"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "trend_forecast",
                "description": "未来贷款利率趋势的预测结果。"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "LoanRate.evaluate_risk",
        "description": "评估贷款利率变化带来的风险。",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "rate_changes",
                "type": "LIST",
                "description": "贷款利率变化列表。"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "risk_evaluation",
                "description": "贷款利率变化带来的风险评估结果。"
            }
        ]
    }
]
如果你已经知道答案，请调用FinishAction来提供最终的回复。
